<title>Llavero</title>
<p>En esta p치gina se explican todas las opciones de uso del llavero en <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>
<section>
    <title>Lado del servidor</title>
    <p>The Keyring feature is backed by the <code>Nickvision.Aura</code> library.</p>
    <p>This library uses SQLCipher to securely store credentials in a platform independent manner.</p>
    <p>The library will use you system's credential manager (i.e. libsecret on Linux and Windows Credential Manager on Windows) for securing the Keyring.</p>
</section>
